name: Cafe Orange Boom

reviews.review_text:
A very relaxed cafe with a great atmosphere and lovey service. The orange juice is fresh! The omelettes were lovely with ample filing (based on what you choose) and made using 3 eggs. The bread is the best and is a locally made one. Must try.
The beef patty based breakfasts sandwich is also good.

Hidden Gem üíé

The place is so amazing. They serve all types of breakfast. I am from Marriott, so know how this works and they were the best place so far serving excellent food. Even the owners come to you for explaining the dish.

The place is super calm. Even the washroom was unbelievably clean, which I have not seen ever, so if anyone looking for a place to have a good time and excellent brunch can come here. You will not go disappointed.

If good, fresh, simple food in a clean, relaxed setting is your thing, this place is highly recommended.

Run by locals, the service is warm, courteous and friendly from the time one enters.

Good menu with reasonable prices.

Definitely not the last time I visit

Well done Team Orange Boom
